data.description: This roomy, thoughtfully updated home, with its mature tree studded yard, is located in one of the most desirable neighborhoods in Edna. 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths with an office that could easily be a 4th bedroom this home is carefully laid out so there is no wasted space! Featuring an extra-large living room and a great kitchen that is open to the dining room and would be the perfect place to share holiday dinners or while the days away playing games around the table. Gorgeous granite, custom soft close cabinets throughout, loads of storage, a nice storage buildings in the back yard and a new covered patio all await you. The A/C unit and hot water heater are both newer, keeping this home energy efficient. Situated on a quarter of an acre, homes in this outstanding Edna neighborhood rarely come on the market so make plans to see this one before it is gone!
